1. *Pričaćemo* o našim planovima za letovanje. (We will talk about our plans for summer vacation.)
2. Rekao je da *pričaćemo* o tome kasnije. (He said we will talk about it later.)
3. *Pričaćemo* o tome kada se sretnemo. (We will talk about it when we meet.)
4. Da li želiš da *pričamo* o tome sada ili kasnije? (Do you want to talk about it now or later?)
5. Već smo *pričali* o ovome. (We have already talked about this.)
6. *Pričajte* mi nešto zanimljivo. (Tell me something interesting.)
7. Da li si *pričao* sa Ivanom o tome? (Did you talk to Ivana about it?)
8. Kada budemo imali više vremena, *pričaćemo* o tome detaljnije. (When we have more time, we will talk about it in more detail.)
9. *Pričajući* o putovanjima, setio sam se jedne anegdote. (While talking about travels, I remembered an anecdote.)
10. Kad god se *priča* o sportu, Nikola ima nešto da doda. (Whenever sport is being talked about, Nikola has something to add.)